<h3 id="transfer-learning-for-sketch-recognition-with-pytorch">Transfer Learning for Sketch Recognition with PyTorch</h3>
<ul>
  <li>Investigated performance of a pretrained VGG16 model on classification of 168 hand-drawn sketches from the TU-Berlin
dataset using PyTorch.</li>
  <li>Modified VGG16 using transfer learning techniques (eg. fixed feature extraction) to achieve higher validation accuracy on
sketches.<br /><a href="https://alyssachen.me/files/pytorch.pdf">[report]</a> <a href="https://github.com/alyssc/Neuro140/blob/master/Neuro140AlyssaChen.ipynb">[Google Colab]</a></li>
